  - `MarketplaceRedistributionOfAcquiringOperation`—acquiring payment;
  - `MarketplaceReturnStorageServiceAtThePickupPointFbsItem`—short-term placement of FBS return;
  - `MarketplaceReturnStorageServiceInTheWarehouseFbsItem`—long-term placement of FBS return;
  - `MarketplaceServiceItemDeliveryKGT`—bulky products delivery;
  - `MarketplaceServiceItemDirectFlowLogistic`—logistics;
  - `MarketplaceServiceItemReturnFlowLogistic`—reverse logistics;
  - `MarketplaceServicePremiumCashbackIndividualPoints`—"Seller's Bonus" promotion service;
  - `OperationMarketplaceWithHoldingForUndeliverableGoods`—withholding for product shortage;
  - `MarketplaceServiceItemRedistributionReturnsPVZ`—reissue returns at the pick-up point;
  - `OperationElectronicServiceStencil`—"Stencils" promotion service;
  - `OperationElectronicServicesPromotionInSearch`—"Promotion in search results" promotion service;
  - `OperationMarketplaceServiceItemElectronicServicesBrandShelf`—"Brand shelf" promotion service;
  - `OperationSubscriptionPremium`—Premium subscription.

